---
import Container from "./Container.astro";
---

<div id="solution" class="w-full">
    <div class="bg-[#0B2843] text-white py-10 w-full">
        <Container>
            <h2 class="text-center text-3xl font-bold mb-8">WHY CHOOSE US?</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <img src="/images/icons/UpFrontPricing.png" alt="Upfront Pricing Icon" class="h-16 w-16 mx-auto mb-4" />
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Upfront Pricing</h3>
                    <p>Know what you are paying for before we start</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center">
                    <img src="/images/icons/Insured.png" alt="Licensed & Insured Icon" class="h-16 w-16 mx-auto mb-4" />
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Licensed & Insured</h3>
                    <p>We’re fully licensed and insured</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center">
                    <img src="/images/icons/NoHiddenCosts.png" alt="No Hidden Costs Icon" class="h-16 w-16 mx-auto mb-4" />
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">No Hidden Costs</h3>
                    <p>No surprises once the job is finished with hidden costs</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center">
                    <img src="/images/icons/experience.png" alt="10 Years Experience Icon" class="h-16 w-16 mx-auto mb-4" />
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">10 Years Experience</h3>
                    <p>We have over 10 Years Experience in the trade so we know what we’re doing</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </Container>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-white text-black py-10 w-full">
        <Container>
            <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center lg:items-start gap-8">
                <div class="lg:w-1/2">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Reliable Plumbing Service You Can Count On!</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg">At My Sydney Plumbing, we take pride in our team of highly skilled plumbers operating throughout Sydney. With years of experience and specialised training, our professionals are equipped to handle a wide range of plumbing issues, from minor leaks to major installations. Committed to delivering top-notch service, we ensure that every job is completed efficiently and to the highest standards. Whether you need emergency repairs, routine maintenance, or innovative plumbing solutions, you can trust our experts to provide reliable service with a personal touch, keeping your home or business running smoothly.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="lg:w-1/2">
                    <img src="/images/plumbing-service.jpg" alt="Plumbing Service" class="w-full h-auto" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </Container>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-white text-black py-10 w-full">
        <Container>
            <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center lg:items-start gap-8">
                <div class="lg:w-1/2">
                    <img src="/images/emergency-plumbing.jpg" alt="Emergency Plumbing" class="w-full h-auto" />
                </div>
                <div class="lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-center">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Emergency Plumbing 24/7</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg">We understand that plumbing issues can disrupt your daily life and cause significant stress. That’s why we offer a full range of comprehensive plumbing services tailored to meet your needs, whether residential or commercial. With highly skilled plumbers operating throughout Sydney, we are able to attend to your needs with a click of a button.</p>
                    <a href="tel:0420701987" class="inline-block bg-[#0B2843] text-white text-xl py-5 px-16 rounded-lg mt-6 hover:bg-[#274066] transition duration-300 call-now-button font-bold">Call Now</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </Container>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .call-now-button {
        font-size: 2rem; /* Adjust the font size as needed */
    }
</style>